<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Trying to use the Visual Studio project provided, I got a pile of warnings, and then errors looking for definitions of HWLOC_VERSION.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Obviously I&#8217;m doing this wrong. Can someone suggest how to build hwloc on Windows?<o:p></o:p></p>
